        <inline name="agenda item name">Proposed programme budget for 2022</inline>
      </p>
      <p>
        <docTitle>Resolution adopted by the General Assembly on 24 December 2021</docTitle>
      </p>
      <p xml:space="preserve">
        <docProponent refersTo="#fifthCommittee">[on the report of the Fifth Committee (<inline name="originating document">A/76/633, para. 60</inline>)]</docProponent>
